OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,FThe family of a "kind and funny"
OL,7,Fmother who was suspected of being
OL,8,Fmurdered by her partner say they want
OL,9,Fan apology from the police after his
OL,10,Fbody was found last week.
OL,12,FKelly Faiers died at the home of
OL,13,FRichard Scatchard in Minehead on 15
OL,14,FOctober. But he disappeared the next
OL,15,Fday after being questioned by police.
OL,17,FFollowing a six month manhunt, in a
OL,18,Fcaravan in Watchet.
