OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,FPolice say they carried out
OL,7,F'significant searches' involving more
OL,8,Fthan three hundred actions and have
OL,9,Freferred themselves to the Independent
OL,10,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC).
OL,12,FBut Kelly's daughters Tania Jackson
OL,13,Fand Jazz Faiers say the family has
OL,14,Fbeen let down by the police.
OL,16,FTania said: "I thought it was utterly
OL,17,Fludicrous how he was found so close.
OL,18,FEven that could have been prevented."
