OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,FJazz said: "No doubt in my mind, they
OL,7,Fallowed him to die. He would still be
OL,8,Falive if they had followed their own
OL,9,Fprocedures. No doubt in my mind."
OL,11,FKelly's children only discovered
OL,12,FScatchard was a convicted sex offender
OL,13,Fby searching for his name online after
OL,14,Fhe disappeared.
OL,16,FPolice said he was considered a risk
OL,17,Fto the public, specifically with
OL,18,Fwomen. He had previously been
OL,19,Fconvicted of sexual offences in which
OL,20,Fhe administered drugs to his victims
OL,21,Fto enable his crimes.
