OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,FAs part of his licence, Scatchard had
OL,7,Fto notify the probation service if he
OL,8,Fwas in a relationship.
OL,10,FAs a result he was wanted for a prison
OL,11,Frecall as well as being wanted in
OL,12,Fconnection with the death of Kelly
OL,13,FFaiers.
OL,15,FTania said: "It all comes back to that
OL,16,Ffirst day. He had broken the terms of
OL,17,Fhis licence and they did nothing.
