OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,F"All the rest of could have been
OL,7,Fprevented. They wouldn't have had to
OL,8,Fdo all the searches, spend all that
OL,9,Fpublic money.
OL,11,F"Somebody chose to let him go, and
OL,12,Fsomeone needs to be held accountable."
OL,14,FJazz said: "A good genuine sincere
OL,15,Facknowledgement and a heartfelt
OL,16,Fapology would be a start. They've put
OL,17,Fus through hell for the last six
OL,18,Fmonths for a manhunt that they've
OL,19,Fcaused."
