OL,3,CPolice failed to stop sex offender
OL,4,Cfleeing after mum's death, say family
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police has said it
OL,7,Fhas kept Kelly's family updated with
OL,8,Fthe investigation at the earliest
OL,9,Fopportunities.
OL,11,FA spokesperson added: "Having received
OL,12,Fa complaint from Kelly's family in
OL,13,FDecember, we made a voluntary referral
OL,14,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC) on Thursday 4 January.
OL,16,FThat process is ongoing and we will
OL,17,Fassist the IOPC in any way we can.
